  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the bell peppers and cook until they start to soften.",
    "Add the cumin, cayenne pepper, and salt. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the temper and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, for 10 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot."
